{"tid":2450682,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Rosé骨瘦如材有驚人肌肉　手臂炸出小山丘⋯網嚇歪：運動量多大","createTime":"2021-03-17T14:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T12:41:51.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"61f4bb80f949a0a419e3d244b106e4e20d349a6e","tid":2450682,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:38:56.000Z","msg":"南韓女團BLACKPINK成員Ros&eacute;近日帶著個人作品《On The Ground》、《Gone》回歸歌壇，歌曲一上線便引來熱烈討論，而她近日積極出演音樂節目宣傳，卻因為手臂上的肌肉掀起另一波熱烈討論，身材瘦歸瘦卻有結實肌肉，手臂一舉起的肌肉量令網友嚇傻，紛紛留言「這麼瘦還有肌肉可能嗎」、「居然有肌肉」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5509/d5509480.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5509%2Fd5509480.jpg&h=7c04b2f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Ros&eacute;肌肉量很驚人。（圖／翻攝自SBS）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRos&eacute;備受討論的畫面，是她14日在音樂節目《人氣歌謠》唱跳的片段，她穿著桃紅色平口洋裝，露出骨感肩膀與四肢，其中一個動作舉起手臂，露出小山丘狀的線條，肌肉量清晰可見，由於她看似瘦若，卻有著意料之外的肌肉，立刻讓網友讚嘆「這樣運動量要多大」、「沒想到有肌肉」、「看到肌肉嚇一跳」，但也粉絲心疼回應「太瘦了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5509/d5509481.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5509%2Fd5509481.jpg&h=b0aeb26b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Ros&eacute;這次回歸被發現更瘦了。（圖／翻攝自Ros&eacute; IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5509/d5509482.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5509%2Fd5509482.jpg&h=3e21b588&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Lisa特地去支持Ros&eacute;的工作行程，但她害羞素顏只露額頭。（圖／翻攝自Ros&eacute; IG）<br />\n<br />\nRos&eacute;這次回歸不僅粉絲熱烈支持，成員Lisa也被拍到現身後台的照片，但她素顏亮相，害羞地將五官全部遮住，反而是露出難得一見的額頭，Lisa過去曾開玩笑表示「露額頭要給錢」，兩人合照曝光後，歌迷立刻虧「珍貴的額頭露出來了」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EUCHYOiPGNA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEUCHYOiPGNA&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT%2BSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=735b14ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EUCHYOiPGNA</a>"},{"pid":"c8aa6f0412c1abf8ef6256d139bdf949351f115e","tid":2450682,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:39:29.000Z","msg":"好靚...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f351fbc9de2e2ba6d76fc23e76fcdc6f1536baad","tid":2450682,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:40:45.000Z","msg":"無波同lady boy有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3fbbb9c154c784ec9f8b4b4ce35d793967dcae","tid":2450682,"uid":289257,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f351fbc9de2e2ba6d76fc23e76fcdc6f1536baad","tid":2450682,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:40:45.000Z","msg":"無波同lady boy有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:44:23.000Z","msg":"ladyboy先正<br />\n夠姣又可以玩佢碌鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc75c0c7729d19726cf321795a1b43c0ab00ecb","tid":2450682,"uid":59522,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc3fbbb9c154c784ec9f8b4b4ce35d793967dcae","tid":2450682,"uid":289257,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f351fbc9de2e2ba6d76fc23e76fcdc6f1536baad","tid":2450682,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:40:45.000Z","msg":"無波同lady boy有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:44:23.000Z","msg":"ladyboy先正<br />\n夠姣又可以玩佢碌鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor